ease date, we&#8217;ve pushed out the 1.0.1 build with a couple of minor changes.  Release Notes for WordPress Facebook Events 1.0.1: Small features, UX and Content Tweaks: Integration with Presstrends. Bug Fixes: Removed unclear/confusing message warning message regarding the need for plugin consistency and added [...]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Rob La Gatta\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1096:\"<p>The response to our <strong>Facebook Events</strong> add-on has been positive since it&#8217;s launch last month, and we appreciate the support from those of you who have bought it. Since today marks release date, we&#8217;ve pushed out the 1.0.1 build with a couple of minor changes. </p>\n<h3>Release Notes for WordPress Facebook Events 1.0.1:</h3>\n<p><strong>Small features, UX and Content Tweaks:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Integration with <a href=\"http://www.presstrends.io/\">Presstrends</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Removed unclear/confusing message warning message regarding the need for plugin consistency and added clearer warnings with appropriate links when plugins or add-ons are out date.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There are a few bugs that have been reported since launch that we&#8217;re still trying to track down, and will hopefully have squashed in 1.0.2 when that releases in August. We&#8217;ve also had a few translation files provided that we&#8217;ll work in there too (and are always looking for more&#8230;let us know if you want to contribute). </p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"http://tri.be/release-facebook-events-1-0-1/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Release: Community Events 1.0.2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:119:\"http://tri.be/release-community-events-1-0-2/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=release-community-events-1-0-2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"http://tri.be/release-community-events-1-0-2/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 17 Jul 2012 01:19:01 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Release Notes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"http://tri.be/?p=21909\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:545:\"As was the case with Eventbrite Tickets 1.0.2, this month&#8217;s maintenance release for Community Events (1.0.2 as well) is also quite lightweight. Make sure you&#8217;ve installed &#38; activated The Events Calendar 2.0.8 &#8212; and Events Calendar PRO 2.0.8, if you&#8217;re a PRO user &#8212; before updating Community.  Release Notes for WordPress Community Events 1.0.2: Small features, UX and Content Tweaks: Integration with Presstrends. Bug Fixes: Removed unclear/confusing message warning message regarding the need for plugin [...]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Rob La Gatta\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1390:\"<p>As was the case with Eventbrite Tickets 1.0.2, this month&#8217;s maintenance release for<strong> Community Events</strong> (1.0.2 as well) is also quite lightweight. Make sure you&#8217;ve installed &amp; activated The Events Calendar 2.0.8 &#8212; and Events Calendar PRO 2.0.8, if you&#8217;re a PRO user &#8212; before updating Community. </p>\n<h3>Release Notes for WordPress Community Events 1.0.2:</h3>\n<p><strong>Small features, UX and Content Tweaks:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Integration with <a href=\"http://www.presstrends.io/\">Presstrends</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Removed unclear/confusing message warning message regarding the need for plugin consistency and added clearer warnings with appropriate links when plugins or add-ons are out date.</li>\n</ul>\n<p> We&#8217;ve gotten some solid feedback from users on the <a href=\"http://tri.be/support/forums/forum/events/community-events/\">Community Events forum</a>, both in terms of feature requests and bug reports, that are helping us improve this plugin with each release. We&#8217;re now hard at work on August&#8217;s maintenance release; the team will be working to patch a couple of long-standing bugs and possibly introduce some new features in that build as well. Stay tuned&#8230;and of course, let us know if you notice anything amiss with the new code once you update to 1.0.2.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"http://tri.be/release-community-events-1-0-2/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"Release: Eventbrite Tickets 1.0.2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:123:\"http://tri.be/release-eventbrite-tickets-1-0-2/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=release-eventbrite-tickets-1-0-2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"http://tri.be/release-eventbrite-tickets-1-0-2/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 17 Jul 2012 01:17:20 +0000\";s:7:\"attri