utes like presenter or equipment needed? Want to Pimp your venues? Got 10,000 events and need an easier way to filter and manage them? Events Calendar PRO has your back!\";s:8:\"category\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:18:\"Eventbrite Tickets\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:48:\"http://tri.be/shop/wordpress-eventbrite-tickets/\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:42:\"http://tri.be/shop/images/147/small-eb.png\";s:11:\"description\";s:596:\"We know that not every event is a free hippie singalong around the campfire. Sometimes you need to make some coin - so we built an Add-On to The Events Calendar that will let you sell tickets using <a href=\"http://www.eventbrite.com/r/wordpressaddon\" targt=\"_blank\">Eventbrite</a>. Never heard of it? As Snoop Dogg would say, its the snizzle diggity. Or as they tell it, Eventbrite empowers you with simple but powerful tools to manage, promote, and sell out your event. It\'s <a href=\"http://www.eventbrite.com/r/wordpressaddon\" targt=\"_blank\">free to sign up with Eventbrite</a> and get started.\";s:8:\"category\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"Community Events\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:46:\"http://tri.be/shop/wordpress-community-events/\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:48:\"http://tri.be/shop/images/143/small-comments.png\";s:11:\"description\";s:426:\"What’s better than throwing a party? Having someone else throw a party for you! Community events is a full featured plugin that allows users to add events to the Events Calendar. You can require user accounts or allow visitors to submit without having to have an account. Want to make sure that nothing fishy is going on? Just turn on moderation! No scary form setup, just turn it on, configure a few options and off you go.\";s:8:\"category\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The Events Calendar\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:45:\"http://tri.be/shop/wordpress-events-calendar/\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:46:\"http://tri.be/shop/images/139/small-events.png\";s:11:\"description\";s:367:\"The Events Calendar plugin is an powerful events management platform for WordPress. This is a FREE plugin on the open source WordPress.org repository. Explore this page for screenshots and a list of features. Want to sell tickets, manage conference schedules, accept user submitted events automatically and more? Check out the available premium and community add-ons.\";s:8:\"category\";s:11:\"Open Source\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:14:\"Widget Builder\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:34:\"http://tri.be/shop/widget-builder/\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:46:\"http://tri.be/shop/images/204/widget-small.png\";s:11:\"description\";s:218:\"Create new custom widgets on the fly! Widget Builder uses native WordPress editing interface to provide a unique tool to build custom widgets for your site(s). The simplest and most versatile plugin we have ever built.\";s:8:\"category\";s:11:\"Open Source\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Image Widget\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:42:\"http://tri.be/shop/wordpress-image-widget/\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:45:\"http://tri.be/shop/images/145/small-image.png\";s:11:\"description\";s:275:\"Add an image, title, description and link to your sidebar in seconds. Simple image widget is a uses native WordPress uploader to add images to your site\'s side-bar. This is one of the most powerful and yet simple widgets in WordPress and currently has over 350,000 downloads.\";s:8:\"category\";s:11:\"Open Source\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"WooTickets\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:30:\"http://tri.be/shop/wootickets/\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";N;s:11:\"description\";s:575:\"Sometimes you want to keep it all in-house, or 